## 4. Admin variable mapping UI pattern

When `templateType === 'yourTemplateKey'`, append a fragment:

```tsx
{templateType === "yourTemplateKey" ? (
  <>
    <SelectItem value="myFieldA">My field A</SelectItem>
    <SelectItem value="myFieldB">My field B</SelectItem>
  </>
) : null}
```

Place it after the shared items (`clientName`, `businessName`, …) inside the same `SelectContent` used for **Template Variable Mapping** (not only the test-template selector).

